%% Job Lifecycle State Machine for Transcription
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> queued
    queued --> in_progress: worker claims
    in_progress --> validating: transcription done
    validating --> published: quality ok
    published --> archived: archive complete
    validating --> failed: validation error
    in_progress --> failed: processing error
    failed --> queued: retry if retries remaining
    failed --> [*]: exhausted retries
    archived --> [*]

